{"tid":962250,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華-香港民間特首","createTime":"2018-12-30T17:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T17:28:19.000Z","uid":22390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52689c5df7852cf40281a7dc5404396a7fe370a0","tid":962250,"uid":22390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181230/59087702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181230%2F59087702&d=g%2F9XyKfhmpymZxUQnmC8AW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a7f9ec93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181230%2F59087702&h=301fff88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181230/59087702</a><br />\n劉德華宣佈取消餘下4場紅館個唱 全面休息<br />\n<br />\n劉德華20場紅館演唱會於本月15日開騷，前晚唱到第14場時，華仔因為喉嚨發炎，在醫生勸喻下被迫腰斬演出，其後大會公佈取消昨晚及今晚共3場演唱會，原訂明晚（31日）大除夕復唱嘅華仔，今晚發聲明宣佈取消之後4場，即由2018年12月28日至2019年1月3日，共7場演唱會。<br />\n前晚華仔在紅館舉行第14場演唱會，唱到第4首歌時因為聲沙關係，在台上喊住宣佈腰斬演唱會，同觀眾鞠躬道歉，其後大會公佈取消28、29及30日共3場演出，希望華仔可以好好休息，並叫觀眾保留完整門票，稍後公佈有關後續安排及退票事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間特首好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔屌你填海啦"},{"pid":"a7d9f0f36aa3eb8b119e56bcbb84665703eead4b","tid":962250,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"炒黃牛果班退到錢既話都算有賺<br />\n買黃牛就死硬 蝕死"}]}